Package alix.util

Class TopArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • alix.util.TopArray
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<TopArray.Entry>
    public class TopArray
extends Object
implements Iterable<TopArray.Entry>
    A queue to select the top elements from a score array where index is a kind of id, and value is a score.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      static class  TopArray.Entry
      A mutable pair (id, score), used in the data array of the top queue.
